item.title: CVE-2020-11056|2024-08-04T11:21:14.644Z -- barrelstrength -- sprout%20forms
item.description: In Sprout Forms before 3.9.0, there is a potential Server-Side Template Injection vulnerability when using custom fields in Notification Emails which could lead to the execution of Twig code. This has been fixed in 3.9.0.
